00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,670
Vice-general Wang.

38
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,200
Your Highness.

39
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:33,150
How's Li's injury? Take him to me.

40
00:02:33,730 --> 00:02:34,580
Yes, Your Highness.

41
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,430
I'm really not a scout.

42
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:44,670
